## test_nosample_chain.med — NoSample with multi-step use inside guard
## Expected: PASS, TAC generated

Organ safeAdd <: Organ x, Organ y :> [:
    Discharge x DosePlus y |
:]

Admission <: :> [:
    NoSample Organ reading |
    Diagnose <: reading MisMatch NoSample :> [:
        Organ doubled =: reading DoseMultiply 2 |
        Organ result  =: safeAdd <: doubled, 10 :> |
        Observe <: "Result: ", result :> |
    :]
:]